'''Max's Flangth House'''<ref name="CSWE" /> was a restaurant that was opened by the [[Ortolan/Legends|Ortolan]] [[Max Rebo/Legends|Max Rebo]] on<ref name="SWI 67" /> the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]<ref name="Epilogue">{{StoryCite|story=Epilogue: Whatever Became Of...?|book=Tales from Jabba's Palace}}</ref> [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] shortly after<ref name="CSWE" /> [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY's]]<ref name="NEC">''[[The New Essential Chronology]]''</ref> [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]].<ref name="CSWE" /> The restaurant was extremely successful and went on to become a chain<ref name="DB">{{DB|character|maxrebo|Rebo, Max}}</ref> with franchises established on seven other planets.<ref name="CSWE" /> Rebo became very rich through the [[flanth-house]]'s success, and he relocated to Coruscant to enjoy a retirement in lavish surroundings and a lot of [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]].<ref name="SWI 67" />

==Behind the scenes==
Max's Flangth House made its first appearance, albeit unnamed, in "[[Epilogue: Whatever Became Of...?]]," a short story written by [[Kevin J. Anderson]] and published in the [[1995]] ''[[Tales from Jabba's Palace]]'' anthology.<ref name="Epilogue" /> The restaurant was first named "Max's Flanth House" in "[[Who's Who in the Max Rebo Band]]," an article [[Rich Handley]] wrote for the [[Star Wars Insider 67|sixty-seventh issue]] of the ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine,<ref name="SWI 67" /> which was published on [[April 15]], [[2003]].<ref name="SW.com">{{SWArchive|url=community/news/2003/03/news20030317.html|text=Celebrate <i>Jedi</i>'s 20th in ''Insider'' #67}}</ref> In [[2008]], ''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]'' went on to identify the restaurant as "Max's Flangth House," which is the spelling used for this article.<ref name="CSWE" />

Max Rebo's entry in the original [[StarWars.com]] [[Databank (original)|Databank]]<ref name="DB" /> and in ''The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia'' state the restaurant was opened after the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].<ref name="Rebo entry">{{CSWECite|III|85|Rebo, Max}}</ref> The restaurant's ''The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia'' entry clarifies that it was opened shortly after the Battle of Endor,<ref name="CSWE" /> which [[2005]]'s ''[[The New Essential Chronology]]'' dates to 4 [[Galactic Standard Calendar|ABY]] and before the Galactic Civil War's end.<ref name="NEC" /> This article treats the restaurant's ''The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia'' entry as correct with regard to the time period.

